original_query: What information can you find in Tesla_Motors_IP_Open_Innovation_and_the_Carbon_Crisis_-_Matthew_Rimmer.pdf?
solution_summary: Tesla initially used patents but shifted to an open-source approach to encourage electric vehicle development and combat the carbon crisis. CEO Elon Musk announced this change. Tesla has a significant patent portfolio related to battery and charging technologies.
